00:00:41.020 --> 00:00:42.010
Sam, take it away.

00:00:42.010 --> 00:00:44.900
SAM ALDERSON: Welcome,
if you're interested in accessibility

00:00:44.900 --> 00:00:47.130
in social media then
you’re in the right place.

00:00:47.130 --> 00:00:51.590
My name is Sam and I work for a
little WordPress called Yoast.

00:00:51.590 --> 00:00:54.260
You'll find me on most of the
networks and I’m Good Plan, Sam

00:00:54.260 --> 00:00:57.320
and I'm obsessed with
